translation[10]{c,v,t}:
  24,44,Allah Taalaa hi din aur raat ko rad-o-badal kerta rehta hai aankhon walon kay liye to iss mein yaqeenan bari bari ibraten hain
  24,45,Tamam kay tamam chalney phirney walay jaandaaron ko Allah Taalaa hi ney pani say peda kiya hai inn mein say baaz to apnay pet kay bal chaltay hain baaz do paon per chaltay hain. Baaz char paon per chaltay hain Allah Taalaa jo chahata hai peda kerta hai. Be-shak Allah Taalaa her cheez per qadir hai
  24,46,Bila shak-o-shuba hum ney roshan aur wazeh aayaten utar di hain Allah Taalaa jissay chahaye seedhi raah dikha deta hai
  24,47,Aur kehtay hain kay hum Allah Taalaa aur rasool per eman laye aur faman bardaar huye phir unn mein say aik firqa iss kay baad bhi phir jata hai. Yeh eman walay hain (hi) nahi
  24,48,Jab yeh iss baat ki taraf bulaye jatay hain kay Allah aur iss ka rasool unn kay jharay chuka dey to bhi inn ki aik jamat mun morney wali bann jati hai
  24,49,Haan agar inhi ko haq phonchta ho to mutee-o-farma bardaar ho ker iss ki taraf chalay aatay hain
  24,50,Kiya inn kay dilon mein beemari hai? Ya yeh shak-o-shuba mein paray huye hain? Ya enhen iss baat ka darr hai kay Allah Taalaa aur uss ka rasool inn ki haq talfi na keren? Baat yeh hai kay yeh log khud hi baray zalim hain
  24,51,eman walon ka qol to yeh hai kay jab unhen iss liye bulaya jata hai kay Allah aur iss ka rasool inn mein faisal ker dey to woh kehtay hain kay hum ney suna aur maan liya. Yehi log kaamyaab honey walay hain
  24,52,Jo bhi Allah Taalaa ki uss kay rasool ki farman bardaari keren khof-e-elahee rakhen aur uss kay azabon say dartay rahen wohi nijat paney walay hain
  24,53,Bari pukhtagi kay sath Allah Taalaa ki qasmen kha kha ker kehtay hain kay aap ka hukum hotay hi nikal kharay hongay. Keh dijiy kay bus qasmen na khao (tumhari) itaâ€™at ki haqeeqat maloom hai. Jo kuch tum ker rahey ho Allah Taalaa uss say ba-khabar hai